Hmm. Not sure about this one. I like the idea that it claims to be constructed by the Foundation, at a site that was never built (if I read that right), but causing insanity in such a large radius seems a bit more on the useful side, especially since it's under Overseer control, theoretically. Also, why did it initially claim to 'terminate' targets, if it doesn't cause death without also causing mass insanity? That's the part that really bothers me: it seems like 57 targets, at least one would be in a major population center.







